255
00:20:24,031 --> 00:20:25,282
Good morning.

256
00:20:26,992 --> 00:20:28,410
Good morning.

257
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:43,090
This is very good work.

258
00:20:45,384 --> 00:20:49,012
Sir, how did you
get a copy of...
It was ignored, I'm sure.

259
00:20:49,888 --> 00:20:50,931
Yes, it was.

260
00:20:54,559 --> 00:20:57,103
That's because
you don't shoot.

261
00:20:57,437 --> 00:20:59,647
